      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly impeccable, mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and no imperfections whatsoever. Inside, the cabin is pristine, featuring leather that looks untouched and all electronic systems functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, providing a smooth, powerful, and quiet driving experience that reflects its meticulous maintenance history. This is a rare opportunity to own a high-end vehicle in virtually new condition.",
