    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of uncompromising caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. With a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original luster, it represents a premier acquisition for the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking an investment-grade vehicle.",
